name: WMC 4 Jeff Finley shirt (unisex)
description: Get the WMC Fest 4 t-shirt, designed by Go Media's own Jeff Finley. Printed by VG Kids using water-based inks on charcoal tri-blend shirts. Super soft and lightweight. The most comfortable shirt you will own. These shirts are printed on Canvas brand #3413C Tri-Blend blanks.

name: WMC 4 Jason Carne Shirt (unisex)
description: Get the WMC Fest 4 t-shirt, hand-drawn by Jason Carne. Printed by Threadbird using water-based inks on navy tri-blend shirts. Super soft and lightweight. The most comfortable shirt you will own. These shirts are printed on Canvas brand #3413C Tri-Blend blanks.

name: WMC 3 Jon Contino Shirt
description:
Get the exclusive WMC Fest 2012 t-shirt, designed by Jon Contino (one of the featured designers this year).  The design harks back to Cleveland's "old industry" past but calls out to this generation's creative class to work together for a better tomorrow. Printed by VG Kids on Charcoal Grey, Tultex Ultra-Blend shirts. Super soft and lightweight. After a few washes the print will blend right into the tee.

Shirts are 0241 Tultex Unisex Blend Tee with a Tear-Away Tag

name: Defy the Hand You're Dealt Poster by Jeff Finley
description:
This limited edition screen printed poster is extraordinary. Designed by Jeff Finley and printed by the Charlie Wagers for Weapons of Mass Creation Fest 2013. 50 signed and numbered prints measuring 19" x 25" on forest green paper.

*Only 50 printed! Very limited quantities!*

name: WMC Thoughts & Ideas Journal
description:
This handmade, letterpressed notebook is the perfect back-pocket solution to jot down inspirations and revelations. Don't worry, this book does not judge! Printed in a variety of colors by Igloo Letterpress. Buy one or a pack of three. Colors vary.  

Journal measures 5" L x  3.5" W

name: WMC Fest 2013 Button Pack
description: A snappy collection of WMC Fest 1" buttons. Choose your flavor and wear all three! Made by the Busy Beaver Button Co.

name: WMC Fest 4 Poster
description: This official double-sided poster for WMC Fest 4 has all the speakers and bands on it to trigger your memories! The size is 11"x17" and would look great on your wall. Printed by Jakprints on standard poster paper.

name: WMC 4 Jeff Finley shirt (women's)
description: Get the WMC Fest 4 t-shirt, designed by Go Media's own Jeff Finley. Printed by VG Kids using water-based inks on charcoal tri-blend shirts. Super soft and lightweight. The most comfortable shirt you will own. These shirts are printed on Bella #8413 Tri-Blend blanks.

name: WMC Coasters - 4 Pack
description:
A four-pack of letterpressed WMC Coasters

Coasters are off white in color and printed on them is: Dreamers, Doers, Makers, Mistakers - Weapons of Mass Creation. Printed with love by Igloo Letterpress.

name: WMC Fridge Magnets
description: Bring home a two-pack of Weapons of Magnetization. Perfect for your fridge to hang up your latest creation. Mom would be proud! Made by our friends at PureButtons.

name: WMC 4 Steve Knerem & Bill Beachy Shirt (unisex)
description: Get this WMC Fest 4 t-shirt, designed by Steve Knerem and Go Media's own Bill Beachy. Printed on black Alternative Apparel basic crew shirts.

name: WMC 3 Dan Christofferson Art Print
description:
This limited edition 4-color letterpress print is extraordinary. Designed by WMC Fest 2011 designer/speaker Dan Christofferson and printed by the Mandate Press for Weapons of Mass Creation Fest 2012. 100 numbered prints measuring 16" x 24" on cream colored 236lb Savoy printmaking paper. Gorgeous! 

*Only 100 printed! Very limited quantities!*

name: Weapons of Mass Creation Journal
description: These Weapons of Mass Creation journals are to die for. These fantastic 3.5" x 5.5" custom journals were part of the WMC Fest 2012 experience. We are selling the leftovers here! Made by Bound Custom Journals exclusively for Weapons of Mass Creation Fest. You can get one journal for $3.00 or a 3 pack for $7.50.

name: Ink Wars 2013 Poster
description: Be the proud owner of the Ink Wars 2013 poster, celebrating the Battle of Cleveland! It's 11x17 on glossy poster paper.

name: Campfire Conspiracy Sticker Sheet
description: These stickers were designed by Jeff Finley for his band Campfire Conspiracy. There are 4 stickers on the sheet. Read an insightful tutorial on the design process here.

name: WMC 4 Jason Carne Shirt (women's)
description: Get the WMC Fest 4 t-shirt, hand-drawn by Jason Carne. Printed by Threadbird using water-based inks on navy tri-blend shirts. Super soft and lightweight. The most comfortable shirt you will own. These shirts are printed on Bella #8413 Tri-Blend blanks.

name: WMC Fest 4 Hands Sticker
description: Score this high quality 6" sticker. Defy the Hand You're Dealt. Artwork by Jeff Finley of Go Media. These gems were screen printed and die-cut by Sticker Robot.

name: Cellar Door Rendezvous 2013 Poster
description:
Poster for Cellar Door Rendezvous 2013 by Jeff Finley. Printed 11x17 on glossy poster stock, this is a very affordable chance to have some extremely intricate hand-drawn work on your walls. 

Poster is shipped in a tube

name: Go Media - Design with Passion Sticker
description: Grab this 4" sticker from your friends at Go Media. Design with Passion is our motto and we're proud to hail from Cleveland, OH.

name: WMC Fest 2012 Poster
description: Get new poster for WMC Fest 2012. This poster is 18x24 and printed on poster stock. Will ship rolled up in a tube. Designed by Go Media.

name: Go Media "GO" logo sticker
description: Get this cute little 2" sticker of the Go Media "GO" logo.

name: Thread's Not Dead Bookmark
description: 100% Handmade in the USA by Brandon Herbel at All Work No Sleep studios. These limited edition bookmarks (only 100 printed) are screen printed on black canvas fabric with a carefully installed grommet and string combo. A perfect companion to your Thread's Not Dead book.

name: Weapons of Mass Creation - Angryblue
description: Get this amazing Limited edition 2-color screen print by Angryblue. All proceeds from this poster go to help raise funds for Weapons of Mass Creation Fest. All posters signed and numbered by the artist. Approx 12" x 24" This poster is shipped in a large size tube to U.S. customers only

name: Thread's Not Dead Stickers
description:
Enjoy these high quality stickers for Go Media's first ever ebook, titled Thread's Not Dead. TND is the essential strategy guide to the apparel industry and these are stickers you can slap onto your computer, guitar, moleskine, whatever.  
You get both stickers that are shown.

name: Phenomena Button Pack
description: Three 1" buttons based on the Dario Argento classic film "Phenomena." Artwork by Jeff Finley and buttons by StandOut Stickers/Purebuttons.

name: WMC Fest 2011 poster
description: Be the proud owner of the Weapons of Mass Creation 2011 poster. Designed by Jeff Finley and representative of the 2nd annual WMC Fest. It's 18x24 on a matte paper stock.

name: Fest 7 poster
description: 18"x18" Hand silk screened poster designed by Jeff Finley. Limited edition of 100 posters both signed and numbered by Jeff.

name: Ted Leo poster
description: Get this hand silk screened print of Ted Leo designed by Go Media's Oliver Barrett.

name: Go Media promo poster
description: Get this throwback 2006 era design by Bill Beachy.  Printed on glossy poster paper.

name: Mr Gnome poster
description: Pick up this beautifully illustrated poster by William Beachy. This hand silk screened print comes in two different color palettes.

name: Sebastien Grainger poster
description: Grab this amazing silk screened print designed by Chris Comella.

name: WMC Fest 2010 poster
description: Snag this limited edition poster for Weapons of Mass Creation Fest 2010. Printed on glossy poster stock.

name: Heartbreaker Poster
description: Grab the Heartbreaker poster illustrated by Dave Tevenal. Printed on glossy poster stock.

name: Miss Kitten poster
description: Grab this hand silk screened poster illustrated by William Beachy

name: "Make This" Poster
description: People who order the "Make This" poster often order multiples to double up and put side by side for a seamless look.  The posters tile horizontally so you can line an entire wall with them!  So snag a few of them in your order.

name: Valient Thorr poster
description: Pick up this hand silk screened poster illustrated by Go Media founder Bill Beachy.

name: Detroit BBQ poster
description: Detroit BBQ Poster. Designed by Oliver Barrett of Go Media. Hand-printed by Pat Cran at shoutoutloudprints.com. Poster is for a Hip Hop event featuring Platinum Pied Pipers and DJ House Shoes. The event was held at Skully's in Columbus, OH on May 23, 2008.

name: We Are Scientists poster
description: Grab this hand silks screened poster designed and illustrated by William Beachy and Dave Tevenal.

name: WMC Fest 2010 Guidebook
description: Snag a piece of history - the first ever Weapons of Mass Creation Fest official 2010 guidebook.  The booklet includes all the featured artists and designs, filmmakers, and bands that participated in the event including Angryblue, Chad Lenjer, Sam Kaufman, Go Media, Dave Dondero, Two Hand Fools, Mose Giganticus, Ry Russo Young, Lena Dunham, Jay Delaney, and more. Get inspired!

name: WMC T-Shirt
description:
Support the Weapons of Mass Creation movement with an official WMC tee.  

Tultex fine jersey shirt, pre-shrunk, 100% cotton
